{"tid":1657222,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"涉荔景站藏彈弓彈珠　19歲大專生准保釋候訊","createTime":"2019-10-16T03:49:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T04:17:56.000Z","uid":241764,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d2463065418f56044df95fab105f99c741f0fd05","tid":1657222,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T03:49:58.000Z","msg":"有網民9月2日發起「港鐵不合作運動」，3名男子被捕。其中19歲大專生被控一項管有攻擊性武器，案件今（16日）在西九龍裁判法院提堂，被告暫毋須答辯。裁判官應控方要求，將案件押後至12月11日再訊，以待進一步調查。<br />\n<br />\n被告連俊雄（19歲）報稱大專一年級生，控罪指他今年9月2日在港鐵荔景站管有一枝彈弓及37粒彈珠。<br />\n<br />\n控方表示，10月4日才收到6段於荔景及荔枝角站的閉路電視片段，亦需要時間化驗控罪書所指的武器，因此申請將案件押後8星期至12月11日，獲裁判官批准。<br />\n<br />\n被告獲准以原有條件保釋，即5000元現金擔保、其間不得離港、須守宵禁令及到警署報到。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20191016/s00001/1571194293430/%e3%80%90%e9%80%83%e7%8a%af%e6%a2%9d%e4%be%8b%e3%80%91%e6%b6%89%e8%8d%94%e6%99%af%e7%ab%99%e8%97%8f%e5%bd%88%e5%bc%93%e5%bd%88%e7%8f%a0-19%e6%ad%b2%e5%a4%a7%e5%b0%88%e7%94%9f%e5%87%86%e4%bf%9d%e9%87%8b%e5%80%99%e8%a8%8a\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20191016%2Fs00001%2F1571194293430%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e9%2580%2583%25e7%258a%25af%25e6%25a2%259d%25e4%25be%258b%25e3%2580%2591%25e6%25b6%2589%25e8%258d%2594%25e6%2599%25af%25e7%25ab%2599%25e8%2597%258f%25e5%25bd%2588%25e5%25bc%2593%25e5%25bd%2588%25e7%258f%25a0-19%25e6%25ad%25b2%25e5%25a4%25a7%25e5%25b0%2588%25e7%2594%259f%25e5%2587%2586%25e4%25bf%259d%25e9%2587%258b%25e5%2580%2599%25e8%25a8%258a&d=TC1Ad7l9MtPLjBCdpR1LVluXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=130d4ae8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20191016%2Fs00001%2F1571194293430%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e9%2580%2583%25e7%258a%25af%25e6%25a2%259d%25e4%25be%258b%25e3%2580%2591%25e6%25b6%2589%25e8%258d%2594%25e6%2599%25af%25e7%25ab%2599%25e8%2597%258f%25e5%25bd%2588%25e5%25bc%2593%25e5%25bd%2588%25e7%258f%2